        "created_at": "2016-06-26T23:15:29.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p><a href=\"http://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=1677141&amp;iNote=5762021\"><strong>2011 Enfield Wine Co. Chardonnay Heron Lake Vineyard</strong></a> <em>- USA, California, North Coast, Wild Horse Valley (6/26/2016)</em><br>\nA few years in the cellar has been very good to this wine, as it has brought better focus, with the lemon and saline elements at the core and a subtle richness around the edges that adds depth and persistence. Brisk finishing acidity makes keeps everything in check. I don\u2019t know enough about the Heron Lake Vineyard to speak to any terroir signature, but this is certainly a lovely wine.</p>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"http://www.cellartracker.com/\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
